UPDATE users SET
                is_admin = ?2,
                admin_password = ?3,
                is_solver = ?4,
                is_banned = ?5,
                category = ?6,
                last_trade_index = ?7,
                total_reviews = ?8,
                total_rating = ?9,
                last_rating = ?10,
                max_rating = ?11,
                min_rating = ?12,
                created_at = ?13
            WHERE pubkey = ?1
